G = 43
A = 45
B = 47
D = 50

p1 = [G, A, B, D]

# Hold notes for 4 beats
for note in p1:
    playNote(43, beats = 4, sustain = 4)
    playNote(45, beats = 4, sustain = 4)
    playNote(47, beats = 4, sustain = 4)
    playNote(50, beats = 4, sustain = 4)

# Loop progression
for loop in range(4):
    playNote(43, beats = 4, sustain = 4)
    playNote(45, beats = 4, sustain = 4)
    playNote(47, beats = 4, sustain = 4)
    playNote(50, beats = 4, sustain = 4)

playNote (71, beats = 1)
playNote (76, beats = 1)

playNote (73, beats = 0.5)

playNote (73, beats = 0.5)

playNote (71, beats = 0.5)
playNote (73, beats = 0.5)
playNote (76, beats = 1.5)
playNote (73, beats = 1)
rest = (1)

for i in range(2):
    playNote (71, beats = 0.5)
    playNote (73, beats = 0.5)
    playNote (76, beats = 1)
    rest = (0.5)
    playNote (73, beats = 0.5)
    playNote (71, beats = 1)
    rest = (0.5)

# Transition to second chorus
playNote (71, beats = 1)
playNote (73, beats = 0.5)
rest = (0.5)
playNote (76, beats = 2)
playNote (73, beats = 1)
playNote (71, beats = 1.5)
rest = (0.5)

# Second chorus ('Will you still love me...')
playNote (71, beats = 1)
playNote (73, beats = 0.5, sustain = 1)
playNote (73, beats = 2.5, sustain = 2)
rest = (0.5)
playNote (71, beats = 1)
playNote (73, beats = 0.5, sustain = 1)
playNote (73, beats = 2.5, sustain = 2)
rest = (0.5)
playNote (71, beats = 1)
playNote (76, beats = 1)
rest = (1)

# Bridge (slows slightly)

playNote (71, beats = 1.5)
rest = (0.5)
playNote (76, beats = 1.5)
playNote (73, beats = 1.5)
playNote (69, beats = 1.5)
rest = (0.5)

# Final chorus (softer, fading)

    playNote (71, beats = 1)

    playNote (73, beats = 2.5)

# Outro (gentle ending)

playNote (67, beats = 3)
